@startuml
[*] --> Idle
Idle --> DiscoveringSessions : job loop
DiscoveringSessions --> ConnectingBot : open voice sessions found
DiscoveringSessions --> Idle : none found
ConnectingBot --> WaitingReady : login not ready
WaitingReady --> CollectingVoiceStates : ready event
ConnectingBot --> CollectingVoiceStates : client already ready
CollectingVoiceStates --> MatchingStudents : collect identities
MatchingStudents --> MarkingAttendance : credential matched
MatchingStudents --> Idle : no match
MarkingAttendance --> ManualSkipped : manual attendance already exists
MarkingAttendance --> FeeSynced : mark bot present and sync fee
ManualSkipped --> Idle
FeeSynced --> Idle
@enduml
